                  Yue Cao and
                  Tao Peng and
                  Shahbaz Pervez},
	title = {A Trust Model with Fitness-Based Clustering Scheme in FANETs},
	booktitle = {23rd {IEEE} International Conference on Trust, Security and Privacy
