                  Huaifeng Bao and
                  Wen Wang and
                  Feng Liu and
                  Guoqiao Zhou and
                  Peng Yin},
	title = {A LLM-based agent for the automatic generation and generalization
                  of {IDS} rules},
	booktitle = {23rd {IEEE} International Conference on Trust, Security and Privacy
